# Privacy Policy for NetMind

*Last Updated: May 29, 2024*

Thank you for choosing to use NetMind ("the App"). This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application and services.

## 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1 Information You Provide
We may collect information that you provide directly to us when you:
- Create an account or profile
- Use our network analysis features
- Contact our customer support
- Complete forms within the App

### 1.2 Automatically Collected Information
When you use our App, we may automatically collect certain information, including:
- Device information (model, operating system, unique device identifiers)
- IP address and network information for analysis features
- App usage statistics and interaction data
- Performance data and error reports

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
- Providing network analysis and optimization services
- Improving and personalizing the App experience
- Sending notifications about your network status
- Communicating with you about our services
- Ensuring the security and stability of our App

## 3. Network Data

NetMind is designed to analyze and optimize your network performance. To provide these services, we need to access information about your local network, including:
- IP addresses of devices on your local network
- Network performance metrics
- Wi-Fi signal strength and channel information

This data is primarily processed on your device. Limited network performance metrics may be sent to our servers for analysis and improvement of our services.

## 4. Advertising

Our App may show advertisements. For this purpose:
- We work with third-party advertising partners
- These partners may use cookies, device identifiers, or similar technologies
- You can opt out of personalized advertising in your device settings

## 5. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We may share your information with:
- Service providers who perform services on our behalf
- Analytics providers to help us improve our App
- When required by law or to protect our rights

## 6. Data Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect the security of your personal information. However, no electronic transmission or storage system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

## 7. Your Choices

You can control your information in several ways:
- Account Settings: Update or delete your account information
- Device Permissions: Control app permissions in your device settings
- Marketing Communications: Opt out of marketing messages

## 8. Children's Privacy

Our App is not intended for children under 13 years of age, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

## 9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.

## 10. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

GitHub: https://github.com/E4rts/NetMind 
